Time/Period version 0.01
========================

Time::Period allows you to put constants in your code that represent periods
of time.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  None.

